name 'programming-fundamentals-postassessment-intro_pilot-2025'
title 'Programming Fundamentals Pre-Assessment'
markdown <<MARKDOWN
Now that you've completed the unit, this assessment will measure your understanding of key programming concepts, including computational thinking, algorithms, variables, loops, conditionals, debugging, and ethical considerations in programming.

- Read each question carefully and **apply what you've learned** to choose the best answer.
- Some questions involve **code snippets**! Make sure to analyze them before selecting your response.
- This assessment is an opportunity to **show your growth**, so take your time and do your best!
MARKDOWN
